::Prowl::

Prowl roars as he feels Menasor grab the back of his neck. He jerks 
his neck forward, escaping the grip, feeling his neck muscles 
extremely bruised and sore. Prowl spins his head around, digging his 
teeth into Menasor's wrist and ignoring the pain that the action 
causes to his neck.

upset, with

with
